com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.snomedrefset

Interface SnomedLanguageRefSetMember

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SnomedRefSetMember
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Rf2RefSetMember, SnomedLanguageRefSetMemberImpl, UnsupportedRf2RefSetMember

    public interface SnomedLanguageRefSetMember
extends SnomedRefSetMember
    Representation of a SNOMED CT language type reference set member. The purpose of this type of reference set member is to support the creation of sets of descriptions for one or more dialects of a language.

    The following features are supported:

    • Acceptability Id

    See Also:
    SnomedRefSetPackage.getSnomedLanguageRefSetMember()
